---
title: BeaconLink Agent Bootstrap Sequence
---

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Admin as Platform Operator
    participant CP as BeaconLink Control Plane
    participant Policy as Policy Engine
    participant PKI as Certificate Authority
    participant Relay as Relay Network
    participant Agent as BeaconLink Agent
    participant Runtime as Runtime Manager
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter
    participant Inventory as Inventory Service
    participant Events as Event Streaming Platform
    participant Audit as Audit Service

    %% =====================================================
    %% Bootstrap Request
    %% =====================================================

    Admin->>CP: Register new managed site
    CP->>Policy: Validate bootstrap request
    Policy-->>CP: Authorization approved

    %% =====================================================
    %% Identity Provisioning
    %% =====================================================

    CP->>PKI: Request agent identity
    PKI-->>CP: Issue X.509 certificate
    CP->>CP: Generate bootstrap token
    CP->>Audit: Record identity issuance

    %% =====================================================
    %% Agent Startup
    %% =====================================================

    Note over Agent: Agent installed at managed site

    Agent->>Agent: Load configuration
    Agent->>Agent: Initialize secure storage
    Agent->>Runtime: Detect runtime environment
    Runtime->>Adapter: Discover runtime capabilities
    Adapter-->>Runtime: Capability inventory
    Runtime-->>Agent: Runtime information

    %% =====================================================
    %% Secure Registration
    %% =====================================================

    Agent->>Relay: Establish outbound mTLS connection
    Relay-->>Agent: Secure session established

    Agent->>CP: Present bootstrap token + certificate
    CP->>PKI: Validate certificate
    PKI-->>CP: Certificate trusted

    CP->>Policy: Evaluate registration policy
    Policy-->>CP: Registration approved

    %% =====================================================
    %% Inventory Synchronization
    %% =====================================================

    CP->>Inventory: Create managed site
    Agent->>Inventory: Publish capabilities
    Agent->>Inventory: Publish runtime inventory
    Inventory-->>CP: Site inventory updated

    %% =====================================================
    %% Initial Configuration
    %% =====================================================

    CP->>Agent: Deliver desired state
    CP->>Agent: Deliver policies
    CP->>Agent: Deliver relay configuration

    Agent->>Agent: Persist desired state
    Agent->>Agent: Configure reconciliation loop

    %% =====================================================
    %% Runtime Preparation
    %% =====================================================

    Agent->>Runtime: Initialize runtime manager
    Runtime->>Adapter: Load runtime adapter
    Adapter-->>Runtime: Runtime ready
    Runtime-->>Agent: Runtime initialized

    %% =====================================================
    %% Operational Readiness
    %% =====================================================

    Agent->>CP: Registration complete
    CP->>Events: Publish AgentRegistered
    CP->>Audit: Record successful bootstrap

    loop Continuous Operation

        Agent->>Relay: Heartbeat
        Relay->>CP: Forward heartbeat

        CP->>Policy: Continuous policy validation
        Policy-->>CP: Authorized

        CP-->>Agent: Desired state updates (if changed)

    end

    %% =====================================================
    %% Result
    %% =====================================================

    Note over Admin,Agent: BeaconLink Agent is now fully registered,<br/>authenticated, continuously reconciled,<br/>and ready to execute deployments.